**Note:**  This JSON utilizes  `imageUrl1`, `imageUrl2`, etc. as placeholders. In a real-world scenario, these would be replaced with actual image URLs.  Also, the specifications section is partially filled.  More specifications can be added using the `component` of type  `10:10214`  following the same pattern as the provided examples.  The `Add to Wishlist` button is included as per requirement, but functionality would need to be implemented separately.  The `product-card` component is a fallback, which will need to be replaced with an actual product card component if the design system contains one.

The `DESIGN_SYSTEM_DATA` contains some inconsistencies (duplicate entries).  The provided JSON uses only unique color and text style entries (the first ones).  The duplicate entries in `DESIGN_SYSTEM_DATA` should be addressed for consistency.
